      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR HUMMER (1) is having his first look at this course. Comes here a last start placegetter at Angle Park in a OPEN (34.70). Form from his last run is proving strong. Overdue and gets his chance. DEEP STATE (8) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at six of 18 starts including seven wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (35.25) over 600m at The Meadows. Tends to go well on this box draw. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. ELITE ONE (2) is a handy dog who jumped from box 8 last time out and scored by a neck at The Meadows (34.76). The form out of his last race has been franked. Likely to be in the finish. LADY NESS (7) warrants respect following a recent placing in a tight finish.",
